        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>English cleric William Buckland worked as a geologist and vertebrate paleontologist. The first Reader of Geology, University of Oxford (from 1819), Buckland is most noted as the scientific discoverer of dinosaurs.</p>
        </bioghist>
